        Description copied from interface: ImgLyFloatSlider.OnSeekBarChangeListener
        Notification that the progress level has changed. Clients can use the fromUser parameter to distinguish user-initiated changes from those that occurred programmatically.
        Specified by:
        onProgressChanged in interface ImgLyFloatSlider.OnSeekBarChangeListener
        Parameters:
        seekBar - The SeekBar whose progress has changed
        value - The current progress level. This will be in the range min..max where max was set by ImgLyFloatSlider.setMax(float) and min was set by ImgLyFloatSlider.setMin(float). (The default value for max is 1.)
        fromUser - True if the progress change was initiated by the user.
